{"tid":383003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得應該立法禁止肥婆食晏","createTime":"2017-09-01T07:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T07:31:26.000Z","uid":28762,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3bce7cb3257831aae269c68c6493b1634b894de7","tid":383003,"uid":28762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:00:17.000Z","msg":"追擊肥婆係因為肥婆真係太影響市容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次食飯時間要搭台 隔離搭著個肥婆<br />\n佢一個人霸左2個位都算<br />\n佢點餐個時仲要叫多飯多送<br />\n心諗不如叫2碟飯俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nd 肥婆成日話要減肥 但係就一日5-6餐 <br />\n食屎咁 乜都倒晒入口 減條毛咩<br />\n<br />\n立左法一黎可以幫佢地減肥<br />\n2黎大家食晏都坐得舒服d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n肥婆唔好諗住入黎駁我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又到3點 夠鐘去食tea la 你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"745a222720e7c70cc8ed37a7ada1bc599f535b90","tid":383003,"uid":28762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:02:00.000Z","msg":"追擊肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62414dc01ac8e05911cac8b1b2fa0078186c49d5","tid":383003,"uid":47797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:02:50.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d7f94d5e9de4c8cb8de76f7bb260ed0a55d99ae","tid":383003,"uid":28762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:05:50.000Z","msg":"肥婆屍都冇人汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a50426b3dc706bf